{"tid":169360,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗食評 - 魚肉燒賣","createTime":"2017-03-24T07:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T11:13:34.000Z","uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31b127a0a1f4881cade1299affdb966db968dbe7","tid":169360,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/1b60933493e3f736567ed9464ac6a2b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F1b60933493e3f736567ed9464ac6a2b8.jpg&h=fb8f0a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 外表滑得濟，好似食緊潺咁，口感奇怪<br />\n<br />\n2. 雖有魚肉成份，但唔好食，魚肉燒賣最緊要食落有陣，油香味，佢完全冇<br />\n<br />\n3. 質感偏硬<br />\n<br />\n4. 8蚊得果5粒俾d咁既貨色我，真係狗都唔屌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6bc1e170c84b80e067d036676f922c4a7fada0","tid":169360,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:05:25.000Z","msg":"講漏左，係林記，完全唔撚掂，都唔明做咩咁鳩多人幫襯"},{"pid":"393d0e33246de6c235149e006aa43357358ae3c8","tid":169360,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:05:51.000Z","msg":"屌你 幾蚊叫阿姐比佢鮑魚你食好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0317e47ac121f4d9d0d58edf19158ce13f6e626d","tid":169360,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:12:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你 幾蚊叫阿姐比佢鮑魚你食好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d1ba25b1c784ba8006fe728b5e6c764216d376","tid":169360,"uid":30828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"紅磡林記？"},{"pid":"f1370471d59b44b323bbf4aac7b2af7e1eafca0b","tid":169360,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,